skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: voice trainer
des:
Welcome to Voice Trainer.The purpose of this skill is to help you practice vocal speech. You can improve your enunciation by talking to Voice Trainer and hearing it repeat what you say.

If Voice Trainer repeats exactly what you said, congradulations!
If Voice Trainer does not, try repeating the phrase with a clearer slower pace. 

Happy practicing speech!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
